"- **MirГ«mbajtja e ListГ«s**: Identifikoni personat nГ« MailChimp por jo nГ« CRM, dhe anasjelltas\n"
"- **Integrimi i Kontakteve**: Shikoni statusin e abonimit MailChimp nГ« faqet e Personit dhe Familjes\n"
"- **Sinkronizimi Automatik**: Lidhet me pГ«rditГ«simet e personit/familjes pГ«r tГ« mbajtur MailChimp tГ« sinkronizuar"

#. plugin:vonage:section:1:content
#: 
msgid "1. Create a Vonage account at https://dashboard.nexmo.com/sign-up (new accounts include free trial credit)\n"
"2. Find your API Key and API Secret on the Vonage Dashboard homepage\n"
"3. Go to Numbers > Buy Numbers and purchase a number with SMS capability\n"
"4. Note the number in E.164 format (e.g., +14155551234)\n"
"5. In ChurchCRM, enable the Vonage SMS plugin and enter your credentials"
msgstr "1. Krijoni njГ« llogari Vonage nГ« https://dashboard.nexmo.com/sign-up (llogaritГ« e reja pГ«rfshijnГ« kredit prove falas)\n"
"2. Gjeni API Key dhe API Secret nГ« faqen kryesore tГ« Vonage Dashboard\n"
"3. Shkoni te Numbers > Buy Numbers dhe blini njГ« numГ«r me aftГ«si SMS\n"
"4. ShГ«noni numrin nГ« formatin E.164 (p.sh., +14155551234)\n"
"5. NГ« ChurchCRM, aktivizoni shtojcГ«n Vonage SMS dhe vendosni kredencialet tuaja"

#. plugin:google-analytics:section:0:content
